title: Vyacheslav Sushkin
text:
Vyacheslav Vladimirovich Sushkin (; born 11 March 1991) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a>.
Career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Second%20Division">Russian Second Division</a> for <a href="FC%20Petrotrest%20Saint%20Petersburg">FC Petrotrest Saint Petersburg</a> on 22 April 2012 in a game against <a href="FC%20Sheksna%20Cherepovets">FC Sheksna Cherepovets</a>.
